<c.white><c.mono_sans>for you, Razik.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1178
00:42:01.478 --> 00:42:04.814 position:19.52%,start align:start size:63.33% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>So, the Federation commander</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1179
00:42:01.478 --> 00:42:04.814 position:29.05%,start align:start size:42.38% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>is your prisoner.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1180
00:42:01.478 --> 00:42:04.814 position:40.48%,start align:start size:21.43% line:73.96% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>RAZIK:</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1181
00:42:04.814 --> 00:42:06.191 position:30.95%,start align:start size:48.10% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I only came with him</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1182
00:42:06.191 --> 00:42:08.734 position:27.14%,start align:start size:53.81% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>so I could have another</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1183
00:42:06.191 --> 00:42:08.734 position:30.95%,start align:start size:46.19% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>chance to kill him.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1184
00:42:08.734 --> 00:42:10.945 position:27.14%,start align:start size:63.33% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>So you could earn your name.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1185
00:42:10.945 --> 00:42:13.698 position:27.14%,start align:start size:63.33% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I've been hoping for, Razik.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1186
00:42:10.945 --> 00:42:13.698 position:44.29%,start align:start size:30.95% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That's what</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1187
00:42:13.698 --> 00:42:15.616 position:36.67%,start align:start size:53.81% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But you taught me well.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1188
00:42:15.616 --> 00:42:16.826 position:19.52%,start align:start size:70.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I know what you're going to say.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1189
00:42:16.826 --> 00:42:20.121 position:36.67%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>so many times before.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1190
00:42:16.826 --> 00:42:20.121 position:44.29%,start align:start size:36.67% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You've said it</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1191
00:42:20.121 --> 00:42:22.957 position:30.95%,start align:start size:46.19% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>In battle there are</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1192
00:42:20.121 --> 00:42:22.957 position:32.86%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>no second chances.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1193
00:42:29.005 --> 00:42:30.840 position:25.24%,start align:start size:57.62% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But you are not my enemy.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1194
00:42:30.840 --> 00:42:32.217 position:44.29%,start align:start size:21.43% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>He is.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1195
00:42:32.217 --> 00:42:33.634 position:38.57%,start align:start size:29.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>(</c.mono_sans></c.white><c.white><c.mono_sans><i> groans</i></c.mono_sans></c.white><c.white><c.mono_sans> )</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1196
00:42:36.137 --> 00:42:39.265 position:19.52%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Kazon-Ogla.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1197
00:42:36.137 --> 00:42:39.265 position:29.05%,start align:start size:51.90% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>My name is Jal Karden,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1198
00:42:45.397 --> 00:42:47.982 position:46.19%,start align:start size:44.29% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You are first</c.mono_sans></c.white><c.white><c.mono_sans><i> Maje</i></c.mono_sans></c.white>

1199
00:42:45.397 --> 00:42:47.982 position:53.81%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>now, Haliz.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1200
00:42:47.982 --> 00:42:49.692 position:30.95%,start align:start size:42.38% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>My life is yours.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1201
00:42:56.449 --> 00:42:59.118 position:30.95%,start align:start size:46.19% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Kill me if you wish</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1202
00:42:59.118 --> 00:43:01.329 position:25.24%,start align:start size:57.62% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>or let me live and I will</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1203
00:42:59.118 --> 00:43:01.329 position:29.05%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>follow you into battle</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1204
00:43:01.329 --> 00:43:02.955 position:29.05%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>whenever you command.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1205
00:43:11.423 --> 00:43:13.216 position:46.19%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Jal Karden.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1206
00:43:16.386 --> 00:43:18.012 position:46.19%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Kazon-Ogla.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1207
00:43:23.726 --> 00:43:27.063 position:40.48%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>does not belong here.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1208
00:43:23.726 --> 00:43:27.063 position:48.10%,start align:start size:36.67% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>The Federation</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1209
00:43:27.063 --> 00:43:29.732 position:19.52%,start align:start size:70.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I will not hesitate to kill you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1210
00:43:27.063 --> 00:43:29.732 position:32.86%,start align:start size:42.38% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>If we meet again,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1211
00:43:31.401 --> 00:43:32.735 position:29.05%,start align:start size:34.76% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I understand.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1212
00:43:39.576 --> 00:43:41.578 position:44.29%,start align:start size:46.19% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Janeway to</c.mono_sans></c.white><c.white><c.mono_sans><i> Voyager.</i></c.mono_sans></c.white>

1213
00:43:41.578 --> 00:43:43.162 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Five to beam up.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1214
00:44:12.691 --> 00:44:15.903 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans><i>A-koo-chee-moya.</i></c.mono_sans></c.white>

1215
00:44:15.903 --> 00:44:21.700 position:21.43%,start align:start size:67.14% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I pray on this day of memories</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1216
00:44:15.903 --> 00:44:21.700 position:29.05%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to speak to my father</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1217
00:44:21.700 --> 00:44:24.954 position:29.05%,start align:start size:50.00% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>the one whom the wind</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1218
00:44:21.700 --> 00:44:24.954 position:34.76%,start align:start size:38.57% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>called Kolopak.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1219
00:44:24.954 --> 00:44:28.833 position:25.24%,start align:start size:59.52% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Father, if you can hear me</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1220
00:44:24.954 --> 00:44:28.833 position:25.24%,start align:start size:57.62% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>among these unnamed stars</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1221
00:44:28.833 --> 00:44:31.127 position:29.05%,start align:start size:50.00% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I ask you to continue</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1222
00:44:28.833 --> 00:44:31.127 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to watch over me</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1223
00:44:31.127 --> 00:44:33.254 position:29.05%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>as you've always done.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1224
00:44:33.254 --> 00:44:38.593 position:23.33%,start align:start size:63.33% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans><i>I ask you also to watch over</i></c.mono_sans></c.white>

1225
00:44:33.254 --> 00:44:38.593 position:32.86%,start align:start size:46.19% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans><i>a boy called Karden</i></c.mono_sans></c.white>

1226
00:44:38.593 --> 00:44:42.096 position:27.14%,start align:start size:55.71% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>who has a difficult path</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1227
00:44:38.593 --> 00:44:42.096 position:40.48%,start align:start size:29.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to travel.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1228
00:44:42.096 --> 00:44:43.556 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans><i>A-koo-chee-moya.</i></c.mono_sans></c.white>

